so named Dmitri, and also addressed by a nickname), and was moved to tears by the recollection....What a marvelous toy store there is on the Champs-Elysées—no comparison with our Czech stores—what trains! ("le plus rapide train du monde des jouets," with a "streamlined" engine and wonderfully made blue cars). I know you have a thousand worries, but still do write me more often!

